metadata.name: Wild Flower Fantasy
metadata.description:
The bright red and orange wildflowers give you a feeling of dynamic energy.  The Wild Flower Fantasy stimulates the mind and energizes the spirit as your eyes feast on the view. 

A few minutes of gazing at the Wild Flower Fantasy refreshes your mind. The splashes of green represent the natural earthy setting of the Wild Flower Fantasy. The blue represents the freedom that often results from the journey of dynamic energy. The Wild Flower Fantasy has a texture that is bold and smooth, yet beautiful. 

Wild Flower Fantasy dazzles your senses as it radiates its dynamic energy.
